comment: Decades of corporate media lies are to blame for this. This is a case of crying wolf too many times.Now the real wolf is at the door. It can be stopped with the correct government action, such as was done in China.
@YemenNewsToday You should mind if you get it, because you can spread it to others who may be more vulnerable. By the time you're 80 there will be a vaccine

@AsaWinstanley But as a very fit 73 year old I really dont mind if I get it.  Probably it would give me immunity so that I will be less likely to catch it at 80.  And if I do die - well I have to die of something.
